Package: swatchbook
Version: 0.3.2
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.10), libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.4), libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.74)
Installed-Size: 1024
Maintainer: Patricio Aumedes <patricioaumedes@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/PAumedes/swatchbook
Description: Markdown-powered style binder for GNOME
 Swatchbook lets you write colour palettes, typography specs, and design
 tokens in plain Markdown and renders them as an interactive swatch canvas.
 .
 Features include live preview, open/save file I/O, auto-save, dark mode
 support, and a responsive layout that adapts to narrow displays.
